data.text:
published on 2020-07-02T19:48:23Z

This is my interview with legendary singer/ songwriter/ guitarist/ producer Ray Parker, Jr., as heard on WBLH radio "Tunes 92.5." Ray talks about his upcoming documentary film, "Who You Gonna Call?" He also reveals how he wrote the 1984 smash hit, "Ghostbusters."

Genre

R&B & Soul
